{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_09_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 恋愛相談があるんですけど",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n恋愛相談があるんですけど、聞いてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nI need some love advice‚ can you listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛相談？　もちろん、アイドルだからって恋愛しちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Love advice? Well‚ it’s not like idols aren’t allowed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いけない訳じゃない。だが、サニピは今大事な時期だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to fall in love. But Sunny Peace is in a crucial period right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛が仕事に悪影響を与えることがあってはいけない\nそれは分かるな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can’t let love negatively impact your work.\nYou understand that‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2412929376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "真面目な顔で何を言ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about with such a serious face?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1000005722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "恋愛してるのは私じゃありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not the one who’s in love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2666672389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "相談したいのは私のファンの恋愛についてです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want to ask is about my fan’s relationship.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9333339055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ファン？　どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your fan? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2000005722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "全国ツアー中に、私達がファンの願いを叶える\nサプライズ企画をすることは知ってますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know we’re planning a surprise event\nduring the tour to grant a fan’s wish‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、私も過去にもらったファンレターから\n叶えたい夢や願いが書いてあるものを探したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I looked through the fan letters I’ve received\nfor ones that mentioned a dream or wish they wanted to come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その中に恋愛相談があったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was there a letter asking you for love advice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1333336513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "はい……恋愛で悩んでるから\n私に恋のアドバイスをしてほしいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… They’re having trouble with love‚\nso they asked me for some love advice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9000015895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "相談してきたのは高校生で、片思いしている先輩に\n告白しようか悩んでいるそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A high school student wrote that‚ and they’re worried about\nconfessing to a senior they have a crush on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3333349228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "その子に会ってアドバイスしたいんですが\n私は告白なんてしたことがないので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to meet them and give them advice‚ but…\nI’ve never confessed to anyone before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0000015895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "こういう時、どんなアドバイスをすればいいでしょうか\n大人の意見を聞かせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this situation‚ what kind of advice should I give?\nI want to hear an adult’s opinion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0000015895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "大人の意見と言われても\n俺も恋愛に詳しい訳じゃないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you ask for an adult’s opinion…\nI’m not really an expert on love‚ either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0005324446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね……{user}さんに\n恋愛相談なんてお門違いですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… It was silly of me to ask\nyou for love advice‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0333344141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "話を聞くなら、もっと恋愛に縁のある人にしないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I want advice‚ I should ask someone with more experience in love…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8999929427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その通りではあるんだが\nはっきり言われるとそれはそれで胸が痛いな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right‚ but\nit kind of hurts to hear you say it so bluntly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1590858458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それなら他のメンバーに聞いてみたらどうだ？\nいい意見がもらえるかもしれないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then how about asking the other members?\nThey might have some good advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.933324178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。みんなで話し合った方が\nいろんな考えが聞けて参考になるかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. It might be helpful to discuss it\nwith everyone and hear different perspectives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.142828919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n恋愛相談のこと、みんなに話してみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay.\nI’ll talk about the love advice with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4333247502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7333313624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.733324178
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.733324178
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "この間、サニピと月ストが全員揃う機会があったので\nみんなに例の恋愛相談をしてみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day‚ Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest had the chance to get together‚\nso I talked to them about the love advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.5999873479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……結論から言うと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… to cut to the chase‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7000041326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.1475879476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "参考になりませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it wasn’t very helpful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1475879476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことだ？\nまともに取り合ってくれなかったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?\nDidn't they take you seriously?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9853206586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.6333395005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "逆です。恋愛相談が盛り上がり過ぎて\n話がまとまらなかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was the opposite. The conversation about love got so heated\nthat we couldn’t reach a conclusion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6460160092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "渚なんて「みんなから恋愛の話が聞けて楽しい」って\nずっと目を輝かせていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa’s eyes were sparkling the whole time‚ saying‚\n“It’s so fun listening to everyone’s love stories!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2333227158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.997458458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "渚はそういう話が好きだよな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa loves that kind of talk…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9999970119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_09_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "それに、人によって恋愛の考え方がまるで違うんです\n例えば、誰の意見かは言いませんが……",
      "translations": {
